  • Constructor Details

    • Airport

      public Airport(String[] data)
      Creates an airport object from an array of strings containing exactly 19 elements, given in the following order:
      • 0: id
      • 1: iata code
      • 2: icao code
      • 3: airport name
      • 4 to 13: address data, see below for more information
      • 14: phone number
      • 15: latitude
      • 16: longitude
      • 17: time zone
      • 18: website url
      Parameters:
      data - array of string containing airport data
